<HEADLINE> Chinese Trade Talks Help Use Of Technological Developments </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TIANJIN, December 5 (Xinhua) -- Today was the last day of
national trade talks in Tianjin Municipality, the largest port in
north China, where 34 key State projects for applying
technological developments to industry were arranged.
</P>
<P>
Tianjin has made a great effort to promote awareness of new
