relations between the two countries, according to Hu Jintao, a
member of the Standing Committee of the Political Bureau of the
CPC Central Committee.
</P>
<P>
Hu, also a member of the secretariat of the CPC Central
Committee, made the remarks today during a meeting with a
delegation from the German Communist Party, led by its Chairman
Heinz Stehr.
</P>
