expressed delight at once again having an opportunity to meet with
him in Beijing. He noted that Germany is the birthplace of Marxism
and the homeland of Karl Marx and Friedrich Engels. He also
pointed to the long friendship between German Communists and the
Communist Party of China.
</P>
