National Congress of the Communist Party of China
</P>
<P>
Stehr said the great changes which have taken place in China
have left him with a deep impression. He noted that the German
Communist Party pays close attention to the future development of
socialism, and hopes to further enhance friendship and cooperation
with the CPC.
</P>
<P>
