<HEADLINE> Hong Kong Shares Open Higher </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, December 5 (Xinhua) -- Hong Kong stocks rose 68.01
points, or 0.59 percent, to register at 11,542.95 points minutes
after the opening of the morning session today.
</P>
<P>
The key Hang Seng Index rose 267.36 points, or 2.39 percent, to
close Thursday's trading at 11,474.94.  
</P>
