spree over Europe in a gala match on the eve of the World Cup
draw at Marseille on Thursday.
</P>
<P>
Romania's Marius Lacatus scored the opener for the Europeans
two minutes into the exhibition match, only to see Colombian
Anthony de Avila equalize in the 17th minute.
</P>
