<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, December 4 (Xinhua) -- Winnie Madikizela-Mandela
today denied all allegations of murder, abduction and torture
made against her before the Truth and Reconciliation Commission
(TRC) at the end of a nine-day hearing in Johannesburg.
</P>
<P>
She said testimony against her was "ridiculous", "ludicrous"
and that witnesses who testified against her were lying.
</P>
